sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User (Browser)
  participant F as Frontend (Next.js)
  participant B as Backend (Go API)
  participant D as Database (Supabase/Postgres)
  participant A as AI Service (Python)

  U->>F: POST /trips (create)
  F->>B: POST /api/v1/trips
  B->>D: INSERT trip
  B-->>F: 201 Created
  F->>A: (optional) POST /ai/recommendations for itinerary suggestions
  A->>B: (via proxy) save recommendations or read user data
  A-->>F: recommendations
  F-->>U: render trip + AI suggestions
